com.biomatters.geneious.publicapi.utilities

Enum StandardIcons

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<StandardIcons>
      • com.biomatters.geneious.publicapi.utilities.StandardIcons
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<StandardIcons>

    public enum StandardIcons
extends Enum<StandardIcons>
    The set of standard icons used in Geneious. Use of these in 3rd party plugins is encouraged to keep the look consistent.

    To load non standard icons, use IconUtilities.
